
### ADMIN LOGIN
POST http://localhost:5000/common-api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email":"admin@gmail.com",
    "password":"admin"
}

### CHANGE PASSWORD
### READ ALL USERS AND AUTHORS (ONLY EMAILS)
GET http://localhost:5000/admin-api/users

### BLOCK OR ACTIVATE USER OR AUTHOR
PATCH http://localhost:5000/admin-api/user-status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email":"prasanna@gmail.com",
    "isUserActive":false
}